{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"08ce2fd8f8","title":"坚决不同意黄白案","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d8e1c34291","index":0,"year":1937,"month":8,"day":18,"articleId":"08ce2fd8f8"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji10","name":"毛泽东全集第10卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji10.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji10":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"4142abf89c","type":"paragraph","text":"坚决不同意黄白案”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji10","articleId":"08ce2fd8f8"},{"id":"2f95b665a0","type":"paragraph","text":"（1937年8月18日）周、叶：黄白案将红军分制出动，其中包含着极大阴谋，坚决不能同意。在根本问题解决后，我军主力（不是全部）决定由韩城渡河决不走陇海线和平汉线","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji10","articleId":"08ce2fd8f8"},{"id":"96231d8161","type":"paragraph","text":"洛毛","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji10","articleId":"08ce2fd8f8"},{"id":"04226a626e","type":"paragraph","text":"十八日[1]黄白案，指国民党政府军率委员会第一部部长黄绍慧和国民党军副南上车，经风陵渡、同蒲路至代县附近下车，到蔚县一带集中。另一师沿陀海路转平汉路，在徐水下车，到莫东玉田、进化一带，开展游击战争。周题来、朱德在南京同国民党该判期间，白槽、黄绍魅提出这一方案。这是毛泽东得知这一消息后，于8月18日和洛南（张闻天）、周恩来、叶剑英发给","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji10","articleId":"08ce2fd8f8"}],"page":{"id":"cf4e2fc442","publicationId":"maoquanji10","articleId":"08ce2fd8f8","start":533,"end":533}}}},"__N_SSG":true}